quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  22,11,"No e yim…ìe …ìen on mo no rewa Alla e dow selindaare; si mo∆¥∆¥ere he…ìii mo o tabitira sabu …óum si jarrabuyee kadi he…ìii mo o waylitoo e yeeso makko, o hayrii aduna on e Laakara on ko …óum tigi woni hayrere …ìanngunde nden"
  22,12,"Himo rewa gaanin Alla kon ko lorrataa mo e kon ko nafataa mo kadi. ∆äum [ko ja≈ãtaa …óoo], ko …óum woni majjere wo…ó…óunde nden"
  22,13,"Himo rewa on mo lorra muu…óum no …ìuri …ìadaade diini nafa muu…óum kan, bonii welddi…óo bonii kadi wuuridaa…óo"
  22,14,"Pellet, Alla hiMo naada …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin Aljannaaji no ila sengo ley majji can…ói …óin, pellet, Alla hiMo wa…óa ko O faandii kon. @Corrected"
  22,15,On won…óo no sikka wonnde Alla wallataa mo ka aduna e ka Laakara; haray yo o fontu …ìoggol faade ka kammu refti o ta∆¥a ngol yo o ndaaru taw si pewje makko …óen ittay ko tikkini kon
  22,16,"Ko wano nii Men Jippiniri nde Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe. Pellet, Alla hiMo Fewna on Mo O faandii"
  22,17,"Pellet, …ìen gom…óin…ìe e …ìen Yahuudinkoo…ìe e Saabi'iyankoo…ìe e Annasaarankoo…ìe e Majuusinkoo…ìe e …ìen sirkoo…ìe, pellet, Alla O seerndoowo hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darngal. Pellet, Alla e dow kala huunde ko O Seedii…óo"
  22,18,"Enee a yi'aali, wonndema Alla no sujjannde Mo …ìen won…ìe ka kammuuli e …ìen won…ìe ka leydi, naange ngen kadi e lewru ndun e koode …óen e pelle …óen e le…ó…óe …óen e daabeeji …óin e ko …óuu…ói immorde e yim…ìe …ìen, ko …óuu…ói kadi wajibike e mu'un Lepte …óen. Kala mo Alla hoyni haray alanaa mo teddinoowo, pellet Alla hiMo golla ko O Muuyi kon"
  22,19,"∆Åee …óoo …ói…óo ko wennjondir…ìe, …ìe wennjondirii fii Joomi ma…ì…ìe …ìen yeddu…ìe non, ta∆¥anoyte …ìe conci immorde e Yiite fatu…óam yuppee ka dow ko'e ma…ì…ìe"
  22,20,Hi…óam honciniree(hayniree) ko woni kon ka deedi ma…ì…ìe e guri …óin kadi
  22,21,No woodani …ìoole immorde e njamndi
  22,22,"Tuma kala …ìe faandii yaltugol nder ton immorde e suno, …ìe ruttee e nder magge, […ìe wi‚Äôanee:] mee…óee Lette sumoowe ngen"